{"_path":"/travel/v005","_dir":"travel","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"香港旅遊景點","description":"旅遊指引 - 香港旅遊","image":null,"sequence":5,"category":"旅遊指引","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"旅行導遊"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-09-11T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"香港旅遊景點"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港旅遊景點"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小紅書 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/668bc4360000000025007986?xsec_token=ABMZ8qbpfAONaPJ8CPXIcOpr_P2Ub2jjF_EZ1urS4cviM=&xsec_source=pc_search&source=unknown"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港必去九大景點"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"坚尼地城"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n位于港岛的西边，附近不仅有香港大学 、西营盘等街拍地点，还有独特的日落海景\n我们沿着叮叮路线一路打卡，收获了不少的宝藏街景\n搭配富士相机 ，妥妥的网红拍照"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"太平山"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n来香港一定要来太平山\n傍晚的时候可以欣赏到日落城市逐渐亮起灯光的过程\n晚上夜景也是更加璀璨夺目我们刚好赶在太阳快落山去 既能看到夜景也能看到日落 超赞的！！！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"海港城"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n走到海港城的网红大楼梯、笑脸装置 还有打卡了好多咖啡店 很出片的地方 拍出来的海也绝美"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"落日飞车"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n这是我来香港特想体验的巴士\n坐上那一刻 整个人都是自由的 在太阳下山时看到日落搭配沿路的风景 真的是一切烦恼全部消失"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港博物馆"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n做为一名艺术生的我，我真的很喜欢去博物馆艺术馆\n直到进去香港博物馆，看到那些展品 艺术品 真的是非常的震撼！！！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港迪士尼"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n港迪真的是我玩下来体验感很好的一次了！！！\n无需排长队和早起，港迪的夏日花车真的好绝还有魔雪奇缘世界，仿佛走进了电影里，真的是太梦幻了！！！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"维多利亚港"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n维港真的好美！ 它是世界上繁忙的港口之一。\n维多利亚港的夜景也是尤为迷人，真的不要错过每晚的灯光秀！！！超棒的！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"油麻地庙街"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n感受香港地道的烟火气 逛了一天，来感受香港的夜生活 整条街上布满了各类地摊与美食小店。超多港式小食咖喱鱼蛋、牛杂、煎釀三宝、碗仔翅等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"铜锣湾"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n香港的心脏地带 想要体验香港的繁华，铜锣湾是不可错过的目的地。这里汇聚了世界各地的购物者，美食家和探险者，是香港的繁华之源。在铜锣湾 尽量避免周末和节假日，这样可以避开人流高峰。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"小紅書 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/66d96b970000000012011ea9?xsec_token=ABEHYB3-vYCfXZ-Q9y1CyHpndrWOm6W9tkJ0bHEKaX4Bo=&xsec_source=pc_search&source=unknown"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港一日遊"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v005-04.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v005-04.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v005-02.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v005-02.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"香港美食"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港美食"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/66cda37b000000001d03a1d6?xsec_token=ABIwof0a5P_Yt_UdMbro9WaEDYslp-6mK1MXvaJbS7hDU=&xsec_source=pc_search&source=unknown"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"尖沙嘴 9 家美食"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/65dea9200000000003036619?xsec_token=AB6L8UhOCDTEIkfMV3nOXSsDy4ELGbK1EVrZnQvTLDuM0=&xsec_source=pc_search&source=unknown"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港美食清單"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港旅遊美食清單推薦"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n【香港美食特集】五天四夜香港行吃了什麼\n先說說五天四夜我們有一整天幾乎花在香港迪士尼，還有同行友人不吃芋頭與杏仁，還有奶味太重的飲品，所以甜品店就較沒去踩點..."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hashtag B (銅鑼灣)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"紅茶冰室(尖沙咀)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"金華冰廳(旺角) 👉🏻 唯一超不推"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"竺扶大班燒味(灣仔)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"珍妮曲奇聰明小熊(上環)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Arabica 咖啡(堅尼地城)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"甘牌燒鵝(灣仔)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SKYE 高空酒吧(銅鑼灣)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港帝苑酒店蝴蝶酥(尖沙咀)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bakehouse 蛋撻(灣仔)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"旺記冰室(灣仔)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Cupping Room(尖沙咀)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"富豪雪糕車"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"媽咪雞蛋仔（上環）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一點心 one dim sum (中環)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"蘭芳園 (中環)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Vission Bakery(中環)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ohlalagout(上環)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"沾仔記(中環)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"福和雍(中環)"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v005-03.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v005-03.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"香港旅館"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港旅館"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://theharbourview.com.hk/tc/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"灣景國際"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 4 星"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"尖沙咀区域"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n这里景点那叫一个集中 👀，尖沙咀钟楼、K11、美术馆、星光大道、天星码头、海港城全都在这一块儿。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港九龙香格里拉"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港梦卓恩"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港朗廷酒店"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港尖沙咀凯悦"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港丽晶酒店"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港半岛酒店"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港瑰丽酒店"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"铜锣湾区域"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n湾仔主要是以会议展览中心为主啦，金紫荆广场和湾仔电脑城也在这，还有崇光百货、时代广场、DFS，平价的、星级的餐厅到处都是。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港君悦酒店"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港瑞吉酒店"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中环区域"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n这里游客相对少一些，但也是热闹非凡的区域哦。米其林餐厅、摩天轮 🎡、叮叮车、太平山 ⛰、山顶缆车、中环半山扶手电梯、兰桂坊、置地广场、IFC 都能在这找到"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港港丽酒店"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港港岛香格里拉"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港 Jw 万豪"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港四季"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文华东方"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"置地文华东方"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"尼依格罗"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"香港奕居酒店"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"v005-05.jpeg","src":"/images/travel/v005-05.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"香港旅遊景點","depth":2,"text":"香港旅遊景點"},{"id":"香港美食","depth":2,"text":"香港美食"},{"id":"香港旅館","depth":2,"text":"香港旅館"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:travel:v005.md","_source":"content","_file":"travel/v005.md","_extension":"md"}